{"id":"6c777624b1b8","title":"关于一个成绩计算与课程选择问题","created":"2022-09-09T18:07:35.000Z","updated":"2022-09-09T18:07:35.000Z","raw":"<p>[迁移自博客园] | 正解来自郭佬，已<a href=\"https://github.com/Chenrt-ggx/ScoreCalculator\">基于 JS 实现</a>并<a href=\"https://chenrt-ggx.github.io/ScoreFrontend/\">适配 React 前端</a>。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"问题说明\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#问题说明\"></a> 问题说明</h2>\n<h3 id=\"问题背景\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#问题背景\"></a> 问题背景</h3>\n<p>保研算加权的时候，除了必选课程之外要自选 5 门一般专业课，由于一般专业课学分不全相同，怎么选可以使加权最大是个问题，如图所示（往届，仅示意）：</p>\n<img src=\"/assets/images/scse-select-rules.jpg\" width=\"60%\" />\n<h3 id=\"问题抽象\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#问题抽象\"></a> 问题抽象</h3>\n<p>给定 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 门课程，第 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.65952em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span></span></span></span> 门课程的成绩、学分、类型分别为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>s</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>r</mi><msub><mi>e</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">score_i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.58056em;vertica