/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 门课中必须参与成绩计算的课程的数量），使加权平均分最大，对于选择的 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">m</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span></span></span></span> 门课，其加权平均分计算公式如下：</p>\n<p class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>m</mi></munderover><mrow><mi>s</mi><mi>c</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>r</mi><msub><mi>e</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><mo>×</mo><mrow><mi>c</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>t</mi><msub><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>m</mi></munderover><mrow><mi>c</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>d</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>t</mi><msub><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">(\\sum_{i=1}^{m}{score_i}\\times{credits_i})/(\\sum_{i=1}^{m}{credits_i})\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.929066em;vertical-align:-1.277669em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><sp