g reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">m</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.277669em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">c</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">r</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">d</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">s</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.31166399999999994em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">i</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<h2 id=\"问题解决\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#问题解决\"></a> 问题解决</h2>\n<h3 id=\"暴力做法\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#暴力做法\"></a> 暴力做法</h3>\n<p>容易发现，全部必须参与成绩计算的课程可以等效成一门课，其学分为必须参与成绩计算的课程的总学分，其成绩为必须参与成绩计算的课程的加权平均分。</p>\n<p>假设 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 门课程中有 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span></span></span></span> 门课必须参与成绩计算，暴力做法即枚举从 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n-p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span></span></span></span> 门课中选出 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">m-p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span></span></span></span> 门课的所有情况，再分别与必须参与成绩计算的课程计算加权平均分，取其最大值。</p>\n<p>本地测试表明，暴力做法可以在可接受的时间范围内计算 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>p</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>16</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n-p&lt;16</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7335400000000001em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\">6</span></span></span></span> 的情况，其可以应对绝大多数日常需求，下文主要讨论理论复杂度更优的算法。</p>\n<h3 id=\"贪心做法\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#贪心做法\"></a> 贪心做法</h3>\n<p>同样假设 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 门课程中有 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span></span></span></span> 门必须参与成绩计算，一个可能的想法是，进行 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">m-p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span></span></span></span> 轮选择，每次从 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n-p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.66666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">p</span></span></span></span> 门课中选出一门可以使加入这门课后总加权平均分最高的课，如此可将时间复杂度从指数级优化到 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n^2)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.064108em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>。</p>\n<p>笔者直观上认为此做法存在正确性问题，但未想到反例也没有给出正确性证明，实现此算法后对拍发现确实存在问题，直观描述为“一门课 A 对总加权平均的贡献大于另两门课 B 和 C，但 A 与 B 和 C 中任意一门课一起对总加权平均的贡献小于 B 和 C 两门课对总加权平均的贡献”，一个反例（<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n=4, m=3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8388800000000001em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.16666666666666666em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">3</span></span></span></span>）如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> courses = [\n  &#123; <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;course 1&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">score</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">85</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">credits</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">optional</span>: <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span> &#125;,\n  &#123; <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;course 2&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">score</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">73</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">credits</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">optional</span>: <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span> &#125;,\n  &#123; <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;course 3&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">score</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">63</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">credits</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">optional</span>: <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span> &#125;,\n  &#123; <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;course 4&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">score</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">73</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">credits</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-attr\">optional</span>: <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span> &#125;\n];\n</code></pre>\n<p>上例的正解为选择课程一、课程二和课程四，此时加权平均分为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>82.33</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">82.33</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">8</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mord\">3</span></span></span></span>，但按照贪心做法，会依次选择课程一、课程三和课程二（已选择课程一时，选择课程三对总加权平均分的影响小于选择课程二或四对总加权平均分的影响），此时加权平均分为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>82.29</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">82.29</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">8</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord\">9</span></span></span></span>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"二分答案\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#二分答案\"></a> 二分答案</h3>\n<p>同样假设 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 门课程中有 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">p</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"