贡献值 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>m</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">limit</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.01968em;\">l</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span></span></span></span>，选择所有贡献值大于 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>m</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">limit</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.01968em;\">l</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span></span></span></span> 的课程，如还有空位再用贡献值等于 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>l</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>m</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">limit</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.01968em;\">l</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span></span></span></span> 的课程补全，熟知查询排名可以通过类似快速排序的做法在 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> 时间完成，因而选择课程的复杂度可达 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>。</li>\n<li>验证结果：显然为 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>。</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>勘误：“熟知查询排名可以…”（Rank）应改为“熟知根据排名查元素可以…”（Nth Element），此外相应做法复杂度的期望是 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>，而不是确定性的 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>。感谢潘老师指出。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>于是按照二分答案的方法，可以在 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>n</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> 时间完成课程的选择。注意事项包括查询排名时需要进行随机化或多点取中防止被有序数据卡最坏复杂度，归位一个元素后需要向两侧去掉相同元素防止被全等数据卡最坏复杂度。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>勘误：条件“<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>r</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>g</mi><mi>h</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>f</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>1</mn><mi>e</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">right-left&lt;1e-4</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">r</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">g</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">h</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.01968em;\">l</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10764em;\">f</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.72777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">e</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4</span></span></span></span>”是否成立由成绩精度决定，当需要得到最优解的时候需要二分到区间长度小于不同方案之间差异的下界，这一下界由学分精度、成绩精度和 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">m</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span></span></span></span> 决定。感谢潘老师指出。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"测试相关\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#测试相关\"></a> 测试相关</h2>\n<h3 id=\"测试暴力实现\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#测试暴力实现\"></a> 测试暴力实现</h3>\n<p>测试边界或异常情况：包括但不限于 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">m</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span></span></span></span> 少于 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 门课中必须参与成绩计算的课程的数量，<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">m</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span></span></span></span> 恰等于 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 门课中必须参与成绩计算的课程的数量，<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">m</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span></span></span></span> 恰等于 <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span> 等。</p>\n<p>测试功能：注意到暴力搜索的过程中，对学分的处理往往不会出问题（出问题的地方更可能是求全组合），测试时可以直接采用相同的学分的测试用例，这样可以方便的得到标答。</p>\n<p>具体实现上，使用 Jest 测试的写法如下，Jest 支持自动进行深比较：</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"js\"><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;check additional aplha&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-function\">() =&gt;</span> &#123;\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> data = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">handmadeAlpha</span>();\n  <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">expect</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">brute</span>(data.<span class=\"hljs-property\">courses</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>)).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">toEqual</span>(data.<span class=\"hljs-property\">result</span>);\n&#125;);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;check additional beta&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-function\">() =&gt;</span> &#123;\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> data = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">handmadeBeta</span>();\n  <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">expect</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">brute</span>(data.<span class=\"hljs-property\">courses</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>)).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">toEqual</span>(data.<span class=\"hljs-property\">result</span>);\n&#125;);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;check additional gamma&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-function\">() =&gt;</span> &#123;\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> data = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">greedyHack</span>();\n  <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">expect</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">brute</span>(data.<span class=\"hljs-property\">courses</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">toEqual</span>(data.<span class=\"hljs-property\">result</span>);\n&#125;);\n</code></pre>\n<p>对于异常处理的测试，Jest 中写法如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"js\"><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;check exception empty alpha&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-function\">() =&gt;</span> &#123;\n  <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">expect</span>(<span class=\"hljs-function\">() =&gt;</span> &#123;\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">brute</span>([], -<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>);\n  &#125;).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">toThrow</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;select number must not less than zero&#x27;</span>);\n&#125;);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;check exception empty beta&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-function\">() =&gt;</span> &#123;\n  <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">expect</span>(<span class=\"hljs-function\">() =&gt;</span> &#123;\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">brute</span>([], <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>);\n  &#125;).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">toThrow</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;selectable course not enough&#x27;</span>);\n&#125;);\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"测试其它实现\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#测试其它实现\"></a> 测试其它实现</h3>\n<p>同样可以完成与测试暴力实现一致的基本功能测试，在此基础上，可以与暴力实现对拍以保证正确性，在通过暴力实现得到标答的情况下，无需构造学分全部相同的特殊测试用例，直接随机足够多组随机测试用例即可。</p>\n<p>需要注意的是，由于可能存在多个可行的解，而暴力做法会优先选择字典序小的解法，二分答案做法会优先选择“贡献值大”的解法，因此此时不可采用类似上文的直接比较，需要采用如下方式，比较选择数量和最终加权平均分是否一致：</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; i &lt; <span class=\"hljs-number\">1000</span>; ++i) &#123;\n  <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;random brute binary test alpha &#x27;</span> + i, <span class=\"hljs-function\">() =&gt;</span> &#123;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> data = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">randomGenerate</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">15</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">6</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">85</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>);\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> std = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">brute</span>(data, <span class=\"hljs-number\">8</span>);\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> ans = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">binary</span>(data, <span class=\"hljs-number\">8</span>);\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">expect</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">calculateSelected</span>(ans)).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">toEqual</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">calculateSelected</span>(std));\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">expect</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">calculateScore</span>(ans)).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">toEqual</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">calculateScore</span>(std));\n  &#125;);\n&#125;\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"一些坑点\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#一些坑点\"></a> 一些坑点</h2>\n<h3 id=\"badge-相关\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#badge-相关\"></a> Badge 相关</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>License 的 Badge 可以直接用，写法如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"markdown\">![<span class=\"hljs-string\">license</span>](<span class=\"hljs-link\">https://img.shields.io/github/license/Chenrt-ggx/ScoreCalculator</span>)\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Version 的 Badge 可以直接用，写法如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"markdown\">![<span class=\"hljs-string\">version</span>](<span class=\"hljs-link\">https://img.shields.io/github/package-json/v/Chenrt-ggx/ScoreCalculator</span>)\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Coverage 的 Badge 是通过 <code>https://img.shields.io/endpoint</code> 生成的，其参数来自于 GIST，可以避免 Badge 进 Repo 的丑陋做法。需要注意的是通过 Github Action 更新 GIST 以更新 Badge 时需要为仓库设置可用于 GIST 的密钥并将 GIST 中对应的内容设置为任何人可见（<s>整了一堆 Badge 之后开始理解你滴勋宗了</s>），参考写法如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"markdown\">![<span class=\"hljs-string\">coverage</span>](<span class=\"hljs-link\">https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https://gist.githubusercontent.com/Chenrt-ggx/cebb88f45886d29a0972f2dd0967f9c8/raw/jest-coverage-comment.json</span>)\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"文件下载问题\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#文件下载问题\"></a> 文件下载问题</h3>\n<p>前端实现中，如果将一个 JSON 资源以 <code>&lt;a href='xxx.json' /&gt;</code> 的形式提供下载，浏览器将识别这个 JSON 并转换为查询参数，因而无法正常下载，一个简单处理方式是将 JSON 资源的后缀名删除或修改为可以下载的类型，再通过 <code>download</code> 字段指定其下载后的文件名，如 <code>&lt;a href='xxx' download='xxx.json' /&gt;</code>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考链接\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#参考链接\"></a> 参考链接</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Chenrt-ggx/ScoreCalculator\">Score Calculator</a>，上文提到的四个算法的 JavaScript 实现，配置了基于 Jest 的单元测试，<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>100</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">%</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">100\\%</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.80556em;vertical-align:-0.05556em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mord\">%</span></span></span></span> 覆盖率。</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Chenrt-ggx/ScoreFrontend\">Score Frontend</a>，基于 React 框架 + Antd 组件库实现的成绩计算与课程选择工具 Web 前端，支持文件上传。</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chenrt-ggx.github.io/ScoreFrontend/\">Score Frontend Page</a>，使用 Pages 服务部署的 Score Frontend 示例。</li>\n</ul>\n","length":"2.5k","time":"10min","categories":["Buaa","Other"],"tags":["JavaScript","Algorithm"]}